node.name: TWUsbEclipseSchnittstellenPlugin
node.shortdescription: A Java Eclipse Plugin for TWUsb inferface for a K8055 board from Vellmann. The framework include a K8055 interface for a board with 5 digital input channels and 8 digital output channels. In addition, there are two analogue inputs and two analogue outputs with 8 bit resolution.
